## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 🔍 **Live Search** | Search any anime instantly with 500ms debounce — no lag |
| 🔥 **Smart Filters** | Trending, Airing Now, Upcoming, All-Time Popular, Movies |
| 📌 **Pin System** | Pin favourites — persists across sessions via localStorage |
| 🔔 **Browser Notifications** | Real push notifications when you pin an anime |
| 📄 **Detail Modal** | Score, rank, episodes, genres, synopsis, MAL link |
| ♾️ **Pagination** | Load more results on demand |
| 📱 **Fully Responsive** | Works on mobile, tablet, desktop |
| ⚡ **No Backend Needed** | 100% frontend — deploy anywhere for free |

