## 🔌 API Reference

This project uses the **[Jikan API v4](https://docs.api.jikan.moe/)** — completely free, no API key required.

| Endpoint Used | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `/top/anime?filter=airing` | Trending anime |
| `/seasons/now` | Currently airing |
| `/seasons/upcoming` | Upcoming anime |
| `/top/anime?filter=bypopularity` | All-time popular |
| `/top/anime?type=movie` | Top movies |
| `/anime?q={query}` | Search |

> Rate limit: 3 requests/second, 60 requests/minute. The app handles this gracefully.

